Package: eCerto
Title: The eCerto package of the Bundesanstalt für Materialforschung (BAM)
Version: 0.1.21
Date: 2021-10-14
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jan", "Lisec", email = "jan.lisec@bam.de", role = c("cre","aut")),
    person("Frederik", "Kreß", role = "aut"))
Description: The package contains a shiny app which provides various functionality to load, process and backup data for the statistical evaluation of analyses conducted during the production of certified reference materials.
